The paper deals with a multi-channel opportunistic communication system, which involves sensing and accessing channels to maximize reward. This problem is relevant to several areas of computer science, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
